: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestSessionHeaderConstant -v`\n154: \n155: - [ ] **T4.4**: Test base_url construction with urljoin\n156:   - Purpose: Verify base_url built from router_url + namespace + agent_name\n157:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n158:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBaseURLConstruction -v`\n159: \n160: - [ ] **T4.5**: Test connection pooling configuration\n161:   - Purpose: Verify HTTPAdapter mounted with pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10\n162:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n163:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestConnectionPooling -v`\n164: \n165: - [ ] **T4.6**: Test bootstrap_session_id success\n166:   - Purpose: Verify GET returns session_id from header\n167:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n168:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBootstrapSessionID::test_bootstrap_success -v`\n169: \n170: - [ ] **T4.7**: Test bootstrap_session_id missing header raises ValueError\n171:   - Purpose: Verify ValueError raised when x-agentcube-session-id header absent\n172:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n173:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestBootstrapSessionID::test_bootstrap_missing_header -v`\n174: \n175: - [ ] **T4.8**: Test invoke with session_id and payload\n176:   - Purpose: Verify POST to base_url with json=payload and session header\n177:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n178:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestInvoke::test_invoke_with_session -v`\n179: \n180: - [ ] **T4.9**: Test invoke headers correctness\n181:   - Purpose: Verify both x-agentcube-session-id and Content-Type: application/json headers\n182:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n183:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestInvokeHeaders -v`\n184: \n185: - [ ] **T4.10**: Test invoke timeout override\n186:   - Purpose: Verify timeout=(connect_timeout, passed_timeout) when timeout argument provided\n187:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n188:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestInvokeTimeout::test_invoke_timeout_override -v`\n189: \n190: - [ ] **T4.11**: Test invoke timeout default fallback\n191:   - Purpose: Verify timeout=(connect_timeout, self.timeout) when timeout argument omitted\n192:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n193:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestInvokeTimeout::test_invoke_timeout_default -v`\n194: \n195: - [ ] **T4.12**: Test close method\n196:   - Purpose: Verify HTTP session closed\n197:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n198:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::TestClose -v`\n199: \n200: ### Phase 5: AgentRuntimeClient Unit Tests (ST-5)\n201: \n202: - [ ] **T5.1**: Test AgentRuntimeClient init with all params\n203:   - Purpose: Verify all init parameters stored correctly\n204:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n205:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestAgentRuntimeClientInit::test_init_all_params -v`\n206: \n207: - [ ] **T5.2**: Test Router URL required raises ValueError\n208:   - Purpose: Verify ValueError when router_url missing\n209:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n210:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py::TestRouterURLRequired::test_router_url_required -v`\n211: \n212: - [ ] **T5.3**: Test Router URL from env var\n213:   - Purpose: Verify ROUTER_URL env var fallback\n214:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_