────────────────\nT1.1, T1.2 ──┬── T3.1 (make_timeout_tuple)\n                          ├── T3.2 (defaults fallback)\nT2.4, T2.5 ──┬── T3.3 (is_retryable_error)\n             └── T3.4 (is_retryable_status)\n\nPhase 4 (Session Headers) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT4.1 ──┬── T7.1 (export)\nT4.2 ──┤\nT4.3 ──┤\n\nPhase 5 (Client Updates) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T1.4, T4.1-T4.3 ──┬── T5.1 (ControlPlaneClient)\n                       └── T5.2 (CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient)\n                       └── T5.3 (AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient)\n\nPhase 6 (Unit Tests) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T1.7 ──┬── T6.1-T6.7 (constants and session tests)\nT2.1-T2.6 ──┬── T6.8-T6.12 (retry tests)\nT3.1-T3.4 ──┬── T6.13-T6.19 (helper function tests)\nT4.1-T4.3 ──┬── T6.20 (header constant tests)\n\nPhase 7 (Export Update) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T1.7, T3.1-T3.4, T4.1-T4.3 ──┬── T7.1 (update __init__.py)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| Phase 1 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestConstants -v` |\n| Phase 2 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestRetryHTTPAdapter -v` |\n| Phase 3 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestMakeTimeoutTuple -v` |\n| Phase 4 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestConstants -v` |\n| Phase 5 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_control_plane.py sdk-python/tests/test_data_plane.py sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py -v` |\n| Phase 6 | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py -v` |\n| Phase 7 | `python -c \"from agentcube.utils import DEFAULT_TIMEOUT, SESSION_HEADER, make_timeout_tuple; print('OK')\"` |\n| All Tests | `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py -v --cov=agentcube.utils.http` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `DEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 120` constant defined\n- [ ] `DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT = 5.0` constant defined\n- [ ] `DEFAULT_POOL_CONNECTIONS = 10` constant defined\n- [ ] `DEFAULT_POOL_MAXSIZE = 10` constant defined\n- [ ] `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` constant defined\n- [ ] `CONTENT_TYPE_JSON = \"application/json\"` constant defined\n- [ ] `AUTH_HEADER = \"Authorization\"` constant defined\n- [ ] `create_session` accepts `timeout`, `connect_timeout`, `headers`, `retry_config` kwargs\n- [ ] `RetryConfig` dataclass with `max_retries`, `backoff_factor`, `retry_on` fields\n- [ ] `DEFAULT_RETRY_CONFIG` with `max_retries=3`, `backoff_factor=0.5`\n- [ ] `RetryHTTPAdapter` retries on 5xx status codes (500, 502, 503, 504)\n- [ ] `RetryHTTPAdapter` retries on `ConnectionError`, `Timeout` exceptions\n- [ ] `RetryHTTPAdapter` implements exponential backoff\n- [ ] `make_timeout_tuple(connect_timeout, read_timeout)` returns `(connect_timeout, read_timeout)`\n- [ ] `make_timeout_tuple` uses defaults when arguments are `None`\n- [ ] `is_retryable_error(exception)` returns `True` for retryable exceptions\n- [ ] `is_retryable_status(status_code)` returns `True` for 5xx codes\n- [ ] All clients (`ControlPlaneClient`, data plane clients) use imported constants\n- [ ] All 20 unit tests pass\n- [ ] `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` exports new constants and functions\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines | Description |\n|------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py` | Modify | +120 | Add constants, RetryConfig, RetryHTTPAdapter, helper functions |\n| `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | Modify | +10 | Export new constants and functions |\n| `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | Modify | -8 | Use imported constants instead of local |\n| `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Modify | -8 | Use imported constants instead of local |\n| `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Modify | -8 | Use imported constants instead of local |\n| `sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py` | Create | ~180 | HTTP utilities unit tests |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Constants Pattern\n\nAll HTTP-related constants should be defined in `agentcube/utils/http.py`:\n\n```python\nDEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 120\nDEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT = 5.0\nDEFAULT_POOL_CONNECTIONS = 10\nDEFAULT_POOL_MAXSIZE = 10\nSESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"\nCONTENT_TYPE_JSON = \"application/json\"\nAUTH_HEADER = \"Authorization\"\n```\n\n### RetryConfig Dataclass\n\n```python\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Set, Tuple\n\n@dataclass\nclass RetryConfig:\n    max_retries: int = 3\n    backoff_factor: float = 0.5\n    retry_on_status: Tuple[int, ...] = (500, 502, 503, 504)\n    retry_on_errors: Tuple[type, ...] = (ConnectionError, requests.Timeout)\n```\n\n### RetryHTTPAdapter\n\n```python\nclass RetryHTTPAdapter(HTTPAdapter):\n    def __init__(self, retry_config: RetryConfig = DEFAULT_RETRY_CONFIG, **kwargs):\n        super().__init__(**kwargs)\n        self.retry_config = retry_config\n    \n    def send(self, request, **kwargs):\n        for attempt in range(self.retry_config.max_retries + 1):\n            try:\n                response = super().send(request, **kwargs)\n                if response.status_code not in self.retry_config.retry_on_status:\n                    return response\n                if attempt < self.retry_config.max_retries:\n                    time.sleep(self.retry_config.backoff_factor * (2 ** attempt))\n                    continue\n                return response\n            except self.retry_config.retry_on_errors:\n                if attempt < self.retry_config.max_retries:\n                    time.sleep(self.retry_config.backoff_factor * (2 ** attempt))\n                    continue\n                raise\n```\n\n### Helper Functions\n\n```python\ndef make_timeout_tuple(\n    connect_timeout: Optional[float] = None,\n    read_timeout: Optional[float] = None,\n) -> Tuple[float, float]:\n    return (\n        connect_timeout if connect_timeout is not None else DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT,\n        read_timeout if read_timeout is not None else DEFAULT_TIMEOUT,\n    )\n\ndef is_retryable_error(exc: Exception) -> bool:\n    return isinstance(exc, (ConnectionError, requests.Timeout))\n\ndef is_retryable_status(status_code: int) -> bool:\n    return status_code >= 500 and status_code < 600\n```\n\n### Client Constants Migration\n\nReplace local constants with imported ones:\n\n```python\n# Before (in each client):\nDEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 120\nDEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT = 5.0\n\n# After:\nfrom agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_TIMEOUT, DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT, SESSION_HEADER\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Constants | T1.1-T1.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Retry Handler | T2.1-T2.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Helper Functions | T3.1-T3.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Session Headers | T4.1-T4.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Client Updates | T5.1-T5.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Unit Tests | T6.1-T6.20 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Export Update | T7.1 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/47 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-029/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-029/proposal.md`\n- Python SDK Design: `python-sdk/design.md`\n- Python SDK Spec: `python-sdk/spec.md`\n- Related AR: `changes/AR-028/tasks.md` (AgentRuntimeClient)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sdk-python/agentcube/exceptions.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sdk-python/tests/test_util